                        <persName role="scribe" ref="PRS00000">ʿAynä Kʷǝllu Gabra Śǝllāse</persName>According to Additio 1, ʾalaqā ʿAynä Kʷǝllu Gabra Śǝllāse (of Qäqäma?) sold the Ms. Probably he is also the scribe.<date>Beginning of the 20th century</date>
